# BhumiRaksha – Planetary Protection Platform

BhumiRaksha is a Waste, Climate and Planetary Intelligence Platform focused on developing systems that transform waste into resources while protecting planetary ecosystems.

The platform explores circular economy models, waste intelligence systems and climate resilience frameworks to support sustainable cities and environmental protection.

## Focus Areas

- Waste intelligence systems
- Circular resource economy
- Waste-to-energy frameworks
- Climate impact analytics
- Planetary sustainability systems

